TRO Learning signs BC TEL courseware pact . TRO Learning Inc said Monday it signed an exclusive agreement to distribute a middle and high school curriculum called Plato via the Internet . TRO said the contract with a division of BC Telecom Inc , the Canadian telephone service provider , will bring Plato interactive courseware to 170 , 000 students in British Columbia as part of computer - based learning network . The partners said Plato courses should be available in 50 percent of the province ' s public schools by 1998 . Financial terms of the agreement were not announced . TRO Learning shares closed up 1 / 2 Monday at 8 - 1 / 4 . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 878 ) ) 
